
'''= " 'virtual meeting place' for CE stakeholders across Europe".'''

URL = http://circulareconomy.europa.eu/platform/en

=Description=

"The European Circular Economy Stakeholder Platform is a virtual open space whose aim is to promote the transition to a circular economy by facilitating policy dialogue among stakeholders and by disseminating activities, information, and good practices on the circular economy. Stakeholders will be able to take part in the Platform by participating in the annual conference and by interacting on the website to look for good practices, to engage with other stakeholders and to share their own good practices and events. The activities of the platform will be coordinated by its Coordination Group. It is supported in its tasks by a Secretariat run by the European Economic and Social Committee (EESC)."

=More information=

* You can contact the European Circular Economy Stakeholder Platform at CEStakeholderEU@eesc.europa.eu and on the hashtag #CEStakeholderEU. 

